50|$|Copyright {{protection}} {{begins when}} a work is actually created and fixed in a tangible form. For the majority <b>of</b> cases the <b>duration</b> <b>of</b> a <b>copyright</b> {{is for the}} life <b>of</b> the <b>copyright</b> owner plus fifty years following his/her death. There are two categories of exceptions to the standard <b>duration</b> <b>of</b> life plus fifty years, however.|$|R
